{"tid":1801329,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"大家記唔記得麥當勞嘅食材來自邊度","createTime":"2019-12-28T14:09:06.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-28T14:11:24.000Z","uid":52417,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"e24cf5b5330ca8f5cb39e4e126c4dfec9009fa41","tid":1801329,"uid":52417,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-28T14:09:06.000Z","msg":"麥當勞講大話　賣出170噸黑心肉<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">2014-07-25  </span></span><br />\n頭條<br />\n【本報訊】香港麥當勞爆出疑用「黑心肉」醜聞。食物安全中心踢爆麥當勞講大話，麥當勞去年至今先後兩次從上海福喜購入脆辣雞腿及吉列豬塊，市民最少把約170公噸懷疑黑心肉落肚。該中心叫停所有內地福喜食品輸港，即時禁售並封存福喜進口食品。麥當勞推搪是發放訊息混亂而致歉，承認另有10種食材來自河北及廣州福喜<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20140725/18811582\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20140725%2F18811582&d=9uLtkTaOKuy%2FgkD%2BHbzoNTbcp9x5SJfJ3tUQBIbvNjo%3D&h=ffc74f8a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20140725%2F18811582&h=31c463b3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20140725/18811582</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/snowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />等我嚟叫醒你哋啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/snowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d6a6d5bc0091dd3e64f1a1b11d086c2800b4fd93","tid":1801329,"uid":52417,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-28T14:09:15.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"5838829ba63d4f37ac5941ea34885517f5354aa5","tid":1801329,"uid":52417,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-28T14:09:25.000Z","msg":"同我咪撚再食麥當勞"},{"pid":"18c46973cc41472c98e90e5e798ea614844eea4b","tid":1801329,"uid":52417,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-28T14:09:48.000Z","msg":"手足都無情講"},{"pid":"e82829f29a5fec08e484b396bb4eff289fb1872f","tid":1801329,"uid":52417,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2